snippet.title: Gta 5 All in One Weapons Location | Story Mode Unlimited Ammo Glitch ( PS5/4, XBox One/X, PC ) 2022
snippet.description:
Hey what's up you guys, im back with another tutorial on Gta V! So today I'm gonna show you how to find Weapons for free in Gta 5 Story Mode(offline) with the exact spawn locations that you can find underneath the sea. Also the glitch shown in the video can be used to collect unlimited ammo for the found Weapons.

You'll find almost everything you need to know upto date because im playing on the one of the latest version which is 1.57(1.58 is the most recent one) and i can ensure that these locations and methods are working across most of the platforms including ps5, ps4, ps3, xbox one, xbox series x, xbox 360 and pc(which im demonstrating).

This is what i found so far

Weapons:
▫️Assault Riffle
▫️Sniper Riffle
▫️SMG
▫️Pump Shotgun 

Explosives:
▫️Sticky Bombs
▫️Grenades

►Leaving a LIKE would always appreciate! 
►Subscribe for latest video uploads! http://bit.ly/29ZRld9

Our social media:
◽Like on Facebook: http://bit.ly/2acp9pO
◽Follow on Twitter: http://bit.ly/6zco6Xb
◽Message on Hangouts: Redux Dreams Lab

Notice:
◽If you encounter sharks when reaching the location, just swim down to the bottom so the sharks will lose you eventually and leave you behind. 
◽It's not necessary to swim too far away from the wreckage in order to respawn Weapons. 
◽Sometimes, you'll find a briefcase which contains handy amount of cash even though switching characters doesn't respawn them as the glitch patched in the latest version.

Thanks for watching and see you back!
